WEBVTT

00:00:00.371 --> 00:00:01.927
Steve Ramirez: Na mojoj prvoj godini postdiplomskog

00:00:01.927 --> 00:00:03.931
našao sam se u sobi

00:00:03.931 --> 00:00:06.231
kako jedem puno Ben &amp; Jerry's,

00:00:06.231 --> 00:00:07.915
gledam neko smeće na TV-u

00:00:07.915 --> 00:00:11.142
i možda, ali možda slušajući Taylor Swift.

00:00:11.142 --> 00:00:12.883
Upravo sam doživio prekid.

00:00:12.883 --> 00:00:14.330
(Smijeh)

00:00:14.330 --> 00:00:16.526
Dugo sam samo

00:00:16.526 --> 00:00:20.342
prizivao uspomenu na tu osobu opet iznova,

00:00:20.342 --> 00:00:22.835
želeći da se mogu riješiti tog osjećaja u stomaku,

00:00:22.835 --> 00:00:25.368
visceralnog „blah“ osjećaja.

00:00:25.368 --> 00:00:27.651
Igrom slučaja sam neuroznanstvenik

00:00:27.651 --> 00:00:30.053
pa znam da su uspomena na tu osobu